{"tid":1455411,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我地已經輸左？無嘢可以做","createTime":"2019-08-12T08:59:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T09:17:03.000Z","uid":285330,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3a117348f6da2728e4256626e254c1b82799bfa6","tid":1455411,"uid":285330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:59:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">梗係唔係</span><br />\n<br />\n首先，你要知敵人係邊個<br />\n唔係黑警，唔係林鄭，而係共產黨<br />\n<br />\n而係香港今次事件中，共產黨已經圖窮匕現，毫無底線<br />\n所有文明國家都已經見到一國兩制名存實亡<br />\n<br />\n香港既國際特殊地位好快消失<br />\n共產黨會徹底失去佢唯一有既，同國際連結既城市<br />\n<br />\n共產黨同美國打緊貿易戰，已經經濟下行<br />\n而無左香港對佢既打擊絕對係一下重擊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">所以大家要做既，係加速國際取消香港特殊地位，徹底焦土化香港去加速支爆</span><br />\n<br />\n堅持落去，if you burn，you burn with us<br />\n香港既民主，只有係共產黨摧毀果日先有機會<br />\n而支爆係第一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ec8da08db8558f652e664920a0effe7b077467","tid":1455411,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:00:28.000Z","msg":"[替天行道]地下勇武行動將無可避免，請各位和理非手足做好不割席覺悟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1454288\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1454288</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"31a74179a1f0fbbeabca7d246029cbdc833687f4","tid":1455411,"uid":284538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:00:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8de7fe1ffa871336f955bfb6220c6c5340693f57","tid":1455411,"uid":284538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:01:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ed0f04b18206d1cf840b5fcb8b1c8aab8560fcc","tid":1455411,"uid":75959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:01:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">未封自己決定去留，封左橋大家記住旅客安全要緊，去T2 保護佢地<br />\n<br />\n泰國黃衫軍，你地大多數人無gear </span></span>"},{"pid":"cc971fc177e78ae62d252efd3164dae3a6cf402a","tid":1455411,"uid":285330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:01:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家做緊既每一步都係將共產黨既遮羞布係國際上撕下，所以每一步都係有用架</span>"},{"pid":"596673dcba4c3d6332a73f7083262fa3c47c7654","tid":1455411,"uid":285330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:04:23.000Z","msg":"每日癱瘓機場 幫香港焦土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92a8c3bc8319953929a6ae2cab0183f91d6cb7af","tid":1455411,"uid":285330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:06:26.000Z","msg":"每日癱瘓機場 幫香港焦土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9354e703966d9c656e58e59f907cb5d466de7183","tid":1455411,"uid":285330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:09:23.000Z","msg":"每日癱瘓機場 幫香港焦土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19192607b25a23f6ebfb94488afd6b3c0a5ec1f4","tid":1455411,"uid":285330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:17:03.000Z","msg":"每日癱瘓機場 幫香港焦土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}